<!-- {{{ Yaf_Action_Abstract intro -->
  <section xml:id="yaf-action-abstract.intro">
   &reftitle.intro;
   <para>
    A action can be defined in a separate file in Yaf(see
    <classname>Yaf_Controller_Abstract</classname>). that is a action method
    can also be a <classname>Yaf_Action_Abstract</classname> class.
   </para>
   <para>
    Since there should be a entry point which can be called by Yaf, 
    you must implement the abstract method
    <methodname>Yaf_Action_Abstract::execute</methodname> in your custom
    action class.
   </para>
  </section>
<!-- }}} -->

